    <div class="forum-post-panel-main clear-block">
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>The Hedgewars team is throwing our hat in the ring with openSUSE for Google Summer of Code 2013!</p>

<p>Pending acceptance, we will be looking for students to assist us with:</p>

<p>* Test Framework Implementation<br />
* Artificial Intelligence Improvements<br />
* OpenGL-ES and WebGL Conversion</p>

<p>Additional information is available at the openSUSE wiki link below.</p>

<p><a href="https://en.opensuse.org/openSUSE:GSOC_ideas#Hedgewars" class="bb-url" rel="nofollow">https://en.opensuse.org/openSUSE:GSOC_ideas#Hedgewars</a></p>      </div>

          </div>
  </div>

