    <div class="forum-post-panel-main clear-block">
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>So. For anyone who is applying through this process.<br />
This is not just applying to Hedgewars, it is also about a proposal that appeals to the mentors under OpenSuSE.<br />
So as well as submitting code to Hedgewars and hanging out in IRC, please try to clearly explain your approach and familiarity w/ the needs of the idea in your proposal.  We'll do our best to help.</p><div class="signature"><p>--<br />
Oh, what the heck.  1PLXzL1CBUD1kdEWqMrwNUfGrGiirV1WpH  &lt;= tip a hedgewars dev</p></div>      </div>

